To prepare a hard-copy version of the manual, use the (pdf)LaTeX program:

(pdf)latex siesta
(pdf)latex siesta
makeindex siesta
(pdf)latex siesta
(pdf)latex siesta
 [+ dvips siesta  if you use plain latex]

Alternatively, you can download a PDF version as:

http://fisica.ehu.es/ag/siesta-extra/siesta.pdf

